# Default code owners for the 7.Exchange organization
#
# This file provides a baseline. Individual repositories SHOULD define their own
# .github/CODEOWNERS to require the right teams on security-sensitive paths.
#
# Owners are requested for review automatically when matching files change.
# Pair this with a branch protection rule: "Require review from Code Owners".
#
# Create these teams in the org (Settings -> Teams) and adjust the handles below.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Fallback: everything is owned by core maintainers unless overridden below.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*                           @7ExchangeDefi/core

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Smart contracts — highest scrutiny. Require the contracts + security teams.
# (Place a repo-specific version of these rules in the `contracts` repo.)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# /contracts/                @7ExchangeDefi/contracts @7ExchangeDefi/security
# /src/facets/               @7ExchangeDefi/contracts @7ExchangeDefi/security
# *.sol                      @7ExchangeDefi/contracts @7ExchangeDefi/security

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Routing / API backend
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# /routing/                  @7ExchangeDefi/backend
# /api/                      @7ExchangeDefi/backend

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SDK & widget (public, supply-chain sensitive)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# /sdk/                      @7ExchangeDefi/sdk
# /widget/                   @7ExchangeDefi/frontend @7ExchangeDefi/sdk

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Frontend app
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# /app/                      @7ExchangeDefi/frontend

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CI/CD and org config — protect the pipeline and these defaults.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/.github/                    @7ExchangeDefi/core @7ExchangeDefi/security
/.github/workflows/          @7ExchangeDefi/security
CODEOWNERS                   @7ExchangeDefi/core
SECURITY.md                  @7ExchangeDefi/security
